snippet.title: Aquaman movie review & cast interviews | Extra Butter
snippet.description:
Where does Aquaman rank in the DC universe? Jason Momoa spills the beans on Wikipedia rumors, Amber Heard talks the importance of a woman who happens to be a superhero, we also hear from director James Wan and Patrick Wilson. Plus behind the scenes footage of Aquaman.

#Aquaman #DCU

Extra Butter Episode 111
